ile:Bronze medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2019 FIVB Volleyball Men's Nations League|FIVB Nations League]]\n\n===Individually===\n* '''2018:''' [[2017\u201318 Polish Cup of men's volleyball|Polish Cup]] \u2013 The Best Setter\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.plusliga.pl/players/id/272 PlusLiga player profile]\n\n{{commons}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Janusz, Marcin}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Nowy S\u0105cz]]\n[[Category:Polish men's volleyball players]]\n[[Category:Skra Be\u0142chat\u00f3w players]]\n[[Category:AZS Cz\u0119stochowa players]]\n[[Category:Effector Kielce players]]\n[[Category:Trefl Gda\u0144sk players]]\n\n{{Poland-volleyball-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox volleyball biography\n| name           = Marcin Janusz\n| image          = \n| image_size     = <!-- Leave this blank for the default size -->\n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Marcin Janusz\n| nickname       = \n| nationality    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland|Polish]]\n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|1994|7|31|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Nowy S\u0105cz]], [[Poland]]\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| hometown       = \n| height         = {{height|m=1.91|precision=0}}\n| weight         = {{convert|81|kg|lb|abbr=on}}\n| spike          = {{convert|326|cm|abbr=on}}\n| block          = \n| college        = \n| position       = Setter\n| currentclub    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n| currentnumber  = 5\n| years          = 2011\u20132012<br>2012\u20132014<br>2014\u20132015<br>2015\u20132018<br>2018\u2013\n| teams          = {{flagicon|POL}} [[PGE Skra Be\u0142chat\u00f3w]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[AZS Cz\u0119stochowa]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Effector Kielce]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[PGE Skra Be\u0142chat\u00f3w]]<br> {{flagicon|POL}} [[Trefl Gda\u0144sk]]\n| nationalyears  =\n| nationalteam   = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Poland men's national volleyball team|Poland]]\n| medaltemplates = \n{{Meda