Ya Fist\",<ref>{{cite web | title=Japan Billboard Hot 100 | url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=hot100&year=2019&month=02&day=11 | work=Billboard |language=Japanese | date=February 11, 2019 | accessdate=February 11, 2019}}</ref>\n\"Welcome 2 Paradise\",<ref>{{cite web | title=Japan Billboard Hot 100 | url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=hot100&year=2019&month=08&day=12 | work=Billboard |language=Japanese | date=August 19, 2019 | accessdate=August 14, 2019}}</ref>\n\"Swag & Pride\",<ref>{{cite web | title=Japan Billboard Hot 100 | url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=hot100&year=2019&month=10&day=14| work=Billboard |language=Japanese | date=October 14, 2019 | accessdate=November 1, 2019}}</ref>\n\"Full Metal Trigger\",<ref>{{cite web | title=Japan Billboard Hot 100 | url=http://www.billboard-japan.com/charts/detail?a=hot100&year=2020&month=01&day=27| work=Billboard |language=Japanese | date=January 25, 2020 | accessdate=February 6, 2020}}</ref>|name=BillboardSingles|group=upper-alpha}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"4\"| 2017\n| \"Lightning\"\n| 2 || 2\n|\n* [[Recording Industry Association of Japan|RIAJ]] <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(physical)</span>: Gold<ref name=\"RIAJ-Jan2017\">{{cite web | script-title=ja:\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u7b49\u8a8d\u5b9a\u4f5c\u54c1\u4e00\u89a7\u30002017\u5e7401\u6708 | trans-title=Works Receiving Certifications List (Gold, etc) (January 2017) | url=https://www.riaj.or.jp/data/others/gold/201701.html | publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of Japan]] |language=Japanese | date=January 30, 2017 | accessdate=October 20, 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"6\"| ''The Rampage''\n|-\n| \"Frontiers\"\n| 3 || 4\n| \n|-\n| \"Dirty Disco\"\n| 5 || 5\n| \n|-\n| \"100 Degrees\"\n| 8 || 11\n| \n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| \"Fandango\"\n| 2 || 3\n|\n|-\n| \"Hard Hit\"\n| 3 || 4\n|\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | 2019\n| \"Throw Ya Fist\"\n| 3 || 5\n|\n* RIAJ <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(physical)</span>: Gold<ref>{{Cite web|u