to\n|[[TV Tokyo]]\n|Episodes 1 & 6\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mdpr.jp/news/detail/1572318|title=EXILE TRIBE\u3001NAOTO\u4e3b\u6f14\u30c9\u30e9\u30de\u3067\u30c9\u8feb\u529b\u30c0\u30f3\u30b9 \u8c6a\u83ef\u30e1\u30f3\u30d0\u30fc\u3068\u30b3\u30e9\u30dc - \u30e2\u30c7\u30eb\u30d7\u30ec\u30b9|website=\u30e2\u30c7\u30eb\u30d7\u30ec\u30b9 - \u30e9\u30a4\u30d5\u30b9\u30bf\u30a4\u30eb\u30fb\u30d5\u30a1\u30c3\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u30a8\u30f3\u30bf\u30e1\u30cb\u30e5\u30fc\u30b9|language=ja|access-date=2019-08-03}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Awards ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Ceremony\n!Award\n!Nominee/Work\n!Result\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2017\n|[[VMAJ|VMAJ 2017]]\n|Best New Artist Video\n|\"''Lightning''\"\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[Asia Artist Awards]]\n|New Wave Award\n|\"''100degrees\"''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" |2018\n|The 32nd [[Japan Gold Disc Award]]\n|Best 5 New Artists (Japanese)\n|\n|{{Won}}<br />\n|}\n== Notes ==\n{{reflist|group=upper-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{Exile Tribe}}\n{{LDH (company)}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rampage from Exile Tribe}}\n[[Category:Avex Group artists]]\n[[Category:Japanese musical groups]]\n[[Category:Japanese pop music groups]]\n[[Category:Musical groups established in 2017]]\n[[Category:Musical groups from Tokyo]]\n[[Category:Japanese boy bands]]\n[[Category:LDH artists]]\n", "name_user": "Sacchan1997", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMembers", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Rampage_from_Exile_Tribe"}
